pful.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20I%20set%20foot%20in%20an%20exam%20hall%20was%20over%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20so%20I%20figured%20that%2C%20at%2032%2C%20getting%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadhd-diagnosis-took-25-years-despite-symptoms-now-feel-better-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformal%20ADHD%20diagnosis%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20be%20pointless.%20I%20made%20it%20through%20school%20and%20university%2C%20I've%20established%20a%20great%20career%2C%20and%20I%20have%20systems%20that%20keep%20me%20on%20top%20of%20things.%20Who%20needs%20a%20label%2C%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20felt%20like%20joining%20the%20ranks%20of%20those%20with%20ADHD%20diagnoses%20in%20my%2030s%20would%20be%E2%80%A6odd.%20Kind%20of%20like%20when%20I%20tried%20rollerblading%20last%20year%2C%20clutching%20onto%20railings%2C%20scrambling%20to%20stay%20upright%2C%20resenting%20every%20child%20that%20scooted%20past%20me%2C%20holding%20the%20skating%20aids.%20The%20tiny%20support%20frames%20were%20built%20for%20them%2C%20not%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20this%20would%20be%20the%20same%20%E2%80%94%20that%20a%20diagnosis%20would%20change%20nothing%20about%20my%20current%20life%2C%20because%20there%20are%20no%20exams%2C%20no%20report%20cards%2C%20no%20teachers%20I'm%20trying%20to%20impress.%20(My%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpilates-instructor-side-job-extra-income-benefits-switched-careers-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epilates%20instructor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20count.%20She%20cannot%20be%20impressed.%20I've%20tried.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2256256600-e09e-4e3c-8b12-a1204e95851a%5C%22%3EI%20learned%20how%20much%20a%20diagnosis%20could%20matter%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20is%2C%20adults%20need%20these%20diagnoses%20just%20as%20much%20as%20kids%20do%2C%20albeit%20for%20some%20different%20reasons.%20Children%20have%20teachers%20and%20parents%20monitoring%20them%2C%20providing%20scaffolding%20for%20their%20daily%20lives.%20Adults%20self-manage.%20No%20one%20is%20bundling%20me%20into%20the%20car%20to%20ensure%20I%20make%20a%20meeting%20on%20time%2C%20and%20if%20I%20miss%20an%20email%2C%20there%20could%20be%20serious%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20established%20things%20to%20keep%20me%20on%20track%2C%20like%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felevated-work-life-with-calendar-mapping-and-annual-silent-retreats-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoded%20calendar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to-do%20lists%20for%20days%2C%20and%20even%20little%20notes%20on%20my%20phone%20to%20remind%20me%20of%20silly%20things%2C%20like%20the%20seafood%20pasta%20at%20a%20particular%20restaurant%20not%20being%20as%20good%20as%20it%20looks%20on%20the%20menu%E2%80%A6because%20I%20forget%20this%20every%20single%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20view%20of%20a%20city%20and%20mountains.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68fb9599c007ca8c273792fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20sought%20a%20diagnosis%20after%20experiencing%20imposter%20syndrome.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Tayla%20Blaire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-executive-combats-manages-imposter-syndrome-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EImposter%20syndrome%3C%2Fa%3E%20led%20the%20charge%20to%20my%20actual%20diagnosis.%20After%20years%20of%20self-diagnosed%20ADHD%2C%20I%20felt%20compelled%20to%20confirm%20with%20a%20specialist%20when%2C%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20I%20was%20invited%20to%20chat%20on%20a%20panel%20about%20visibility%20strategies%20for%20those%20with%20ADHD.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20accept%20the%20invitation%20unless%20I%20truly%20belonged%20to%20this%20community%20that%20I%20suspected%20I%20was%20part%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%2090-minute%20consultation%20and%20assessment%20with%20a%20psychiatrist%2C%20it%20was%20official.%20I%20was%20surprised%20at%20how%20quick%20the%20process%20was.%20I%20was%20even%20more%20surprised%20at%20the%20feeling%20of%20compassion%20that%20now%20materialized%20every%20time%20I'd%20wonder%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20am%20I%20like%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227dcc04ae-bf1f-4e89-91b8-28c638ce8bca%5C%22%3EIt's%20helped%20me%20sharpen%20my%20coping%20skills%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20less%20like%20an%20idiot%20every%20time%20I'd%20forget%20what%20I%20was%20saying%20mid-sentence%20because%20something%20distracted%20me.%20I%20started%20to%20identify%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktoker-time-blindness-struggling-viral-backlash-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etime-blind%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20really%20am%2C%20seeing%20my%20incomplete%20to-do%20list%20as%20an%20inevitability%20because%20I%20always%20try%20to%20pack%20too%20much%20into%20a%20single%20day.%20I%20now%20try%20to%20put%20the%20brakes%20on%20every%20time%20I%20get%20really%20excited%20about%20something%2C%20like%20when%20I%20qualified%20as%20a%20scuba%20diver%20and%20bought%20a%20stack%20of%20new%20gear%20that%20mostly%20sits%20in%20my%20closet%20now.%20I%20can%20see%20procrastination%20as%20my%20executive%20functioning%20having%20a%20'moment%2C'%20rather%20than%20bashing%20myself%20about%20laziness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20exams%20in%20sight%20(thank%20heavens%20for%20small%20mercies)%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20I%20don't%20reap%20the%20benefits%20of%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Forganized-productive-hid-adhd-diagnosis-adulthood-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elate-in-life%20ADHD%20diagnosis%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20tempting%20to%20get%20lost%20in%20'what%20if'%20%E2%80%94%20what%20if%20I'd%20been%20diagnosed%20as%20a%20kid%3F%20Would%20school%20have%20felt%20easier%3F%20Would%20I%20have%20chosen%20my%20university%20courses%20differently%3F%20Would%20my%20work%20life%20have%20turned%20out%20another%20way%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20speculate%2C%20but%20there's%20little%20point.%20I'm%20finding%20strength%20in%20community%20(I%20recently%20asked%20my%20Instagram%20followers%20who%20has%20an%20ADHD%20diagnosis%20and%20there%20are%20so%20many%20more%20of%20us%20than%20I%20thought)%2C%20and%20I'm%20loving%20learning%20about%20the%20strengths%20and%20challenges%20that%20being%20ADHD%20holds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadhd-diagnosis-later-life-after-finishing-school-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1761557822000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68fb956a0be9845f2dc50acc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadhd-diagnosis-later-life-after-finishing-school-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20thought%20it%20wasn't%20worth%20seeking%20an%20ADHD%20diagnosis%20since%20I%20was%20done%20with%20school.%20I%20was%20wrong%2C%20and%20a%20late%20diagnosis%20at%2032%20is%20better%20than%20never.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Tayla%20Blaire)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadhd-diagnosis-later-life-after-finishing-school-2025-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BKashmir%20Sings%20Back%20Voice%20Of%20Truth%26quot%3B%3A%20NDTV%20Good%20Times%20Displays%20Valley's%20Spirit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22NDTV%20Good%20Times%20'Music%20and%20Freedom'%20concert%20was%20held%20at%20the%20Sher-i-Kashmir%20International%20Conference%20Centre%20(SKICC)%20by%20the%20Dal%20Lake%20in%20Srinagar.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1761557752000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-10%2F3vuljof_ndtv-good-t