f2dc51426%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20woman%20with%20a%20purple%20umbrella%20walks%20past%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20on%20October%2013.%3Cp%3ESpencer%20Platt%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStill%20looking%20for%20an%20AI%20trade%20here%3F%20Hsu%20has%20you%20covered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20thesis%20is%20we're%20probably%20in%20the%205th%20inning%20in%20terms%20of%20this%20AI%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BCertainly%20there's%20FOMO%2C%20bubble%2C%20high%20valuation%2C%20and%20all%20of%20that%2C%20but%20we're%205th%20inning%2C%20which%20means%20I%20don't%20see%20danger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHsu%2C%20who%20holds%20the%20following%20stocks%20in%20a%20fund%20he%20manages%2C%20said%20he'd%20put%20%246%2C000%20of%20the%20funds%20into%20Chinese%20AI%20stocks%20and%20%244%2C000%20into%20US%20AI%20stocks.%20For%20the%20Chinese%20portion%20of%20the%20funds%2C%20he'd%20put%20%244%2C000%20into%20online%20marketplace%20firm%20Alibaba%20and%20%242%2C000%20into%20Xiaomi%2C%20which%20produces%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I'm%20looking%20at%20are%20AI-related%20tech%20companies%20in%20emerging%20Asia.%20That's%20largely%20gonna%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20big%20Chinese%20tech%20firms%20that%20are%20trading%20at%20one-third%20to%20one-fifth%20of%20US%20tech%20valuations%2C%20and%20they're%20coming%20out%20with%20things%20that%20rival%26quot%3B%20US%20products%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20US%20side%2C%20he'd%20put%20%242%2C000%20into%20Super%20Micro%20(SMCI)%20for%20its%20AI%20servers%20and%20relatively%20small%20size%20still.%20The%20other%20%242%2C000%20he'd%20put%20into%20Microsoft%2C%20given%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-microsoft-tentative-deal-reached-mou-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexposure%20to%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20that's%20a%20big%2C%20boring%2C%20giant%20name%2C%20but%20it%20is%20so%20tied%20in%20with%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20OpenAI%20is%20still%20kind%20of%20at%20the%20center%20of%20everything%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20probably%20the%20highest%20probability%20to%20be%20the%20winner%20in%20this%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDavid%20Lefkowitz%2C%20head%20of%20US%20equities%2C%20UBS%20Global%20Wealth%20Management%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225329%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20trader%20works%20at%20his%20desk%20in%20front%20of%20many%20screen%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68fbd4b9c007ca8c27379c71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222665%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20trader%20works%20at%20his%20desk%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20in%20New%20York%20on%20October%207%2C%202025.%3Cp%3ETIMOTHY%20A.%20CLARY%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELefkowitz%20also%20thinks%20the%20AI%20trade%20still%20has%20legs%20despite%20concerns%20about%20a%20bubble.%20He%20highlighted%20%26quot%3Bcompanies%20leveraged%20to%20the%20build-out%20of%20infrastructure%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20on%20the%20semiconductor%20side%20or%20some%20of%20the%20industrial%20companies%20related%20to%20providing%20industrial%20infrastructure%2C%20power%2C%20transformers%2C%20and%20so%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20couldn't%20share%20individual%20stocks%2C%20he%20said%20the%20tech%2C%20communications%20services%2C%20and%20utilities%20sectors%20offer%20the%20best%20exposure%20to%20this%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20mentioned%20healthcare%20as%20a%20way%20to%20counterbalance%20the%20tilt%20toward%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20adds%20diversification%20to%20the%20portfolio%20because%20it's%20been%20a%20laggard%2C%20and%20there's%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20policy%20uncertainty%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20nearing%20its%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20also%20pockets%20within%20healthcare%20%E2%80%94%20like%20managed%20care%20%E2%80%94%20that%20have%20had%20some%20issues%2C%20but%20we%20think%20those%20will%20start%20to%20normalize%20next%20year.%20That's%20a%20laggard%20part%20of%20the%20market%20that%20offers%20nice%20diversification%20benefits%20to%20the%20more%20AI-levered%20recommendations%20we%20have.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExamples%20of%20funds%20with%20exposure%20to%20the%20above%20trades%20include%20the%20Vanguard%20Information%20Technology%20Index%20Fund%20ETF%20(VGT)%2C%20the%20Communication%20Services%20Select%20Sector%20SPDR%20ETF%20Fund%20(XLC)%2C%20the%20Vanguard%20Utilities%20ETF%20(VPU)%2C%20and%20the%20iShares%20U.S.%20Healthcare%20ETF%20(IYH).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETony%20Despirito%2C%20global%20CIO%20for%20fundamental%20equities%20at%20BlackRock%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226688%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20walk%20past%20the%20BlackRock%20office%20building%20during%20a%20rainstorm%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68fbd4c50be9845f2dc5142f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223344%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeople%20walk%20past%20the%20BlackRoc%20building%20at%2050%20Hudson%20Yards%20during%20a%20rainstorm%20on%20August%2004%2C%202024%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3Cp%3ECraig%20T%20Fruchtman%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDeSpirito%20said%20he'd%20look%20for%20beat-up%20names%20to%20put%20money%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20themes%20I%20look%20for%20is%20what%20I%20call%20'trough%20on%20trough.'%20That%20means%20a%20company%20where%20earnings%20are%20at%20trough%20levels%20%E2%80%94%20so%20there's%20good%20earnings%20growth%20ahead%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20multiple%20is%20also%20low%20relative%20to%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20get%20two%20ways%20to%20win%3A%20through%20earnings%20growth%20and%20multiple%20expansion.%20Those%20have%20been%20some%20of%20my%20best%20investments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20highlighted%20a%20few%20cheap%20parts%20of%20the%20market%20he%20sees%20right%20now%2C%20the%20first%20being%20health%20maintenance%20organization%20(HMO)%20stocks%20%E2%80%94%20essentially%20firms%20offering%20insurance%20plans.%20We're%20at%20a%20low-point%20in%20the%20underwriting%20cycle%2C%20he%20said%2C%20meaning%20underwriting%20is%20going%20to%20get%20stricter%2C%20leading%20to%20larger%20profit%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Elevance%20Health%20is%20an%20example%20of%20an%20attractive%20HMO%2C%20trading%20at%2011.5%20times%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20he%20likes%20firms%20tied%20to%20housing%20turnover%2C%20or%20increasing%20numbers%20of%20people%20moving%2C%20as%20interest%20rates%20come%20down.%20For%20example%2C%20plumbing%20firms%20benefit%20from%20higher%20turnover%2C%20as%20fixtures%20are%20frequently%20replaced.%20Fortune%20Brands%20is%20a%20cheap%20stock%20well-positioned%20to%20capitalize%20on%20this%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20he%20likes%20stocks%20that%20trade%20at%20a%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bheadquarter%20discount%2C%26quot%3B%20meaning%20they're%20cheap%20simply%20because%20they're%20based%20outside%20of%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20BP%20and%20Shell%20trade%20at%20significant%20P%2FE%20discounts%20to%20Exxon%2C%20despite%20being%20similar%20businesses%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBritish%20American%20Tobacco%20trades%20at%20the%20same%20price%20as%20Altria%2C%20but%20it's%20got%20more%20next-gen%20products%20(vapes%2C%20nicotine%20pouches)%20growing%20at%2015%25%20a%20year%2C%20plus%20an%20Indian%20subsidiary%20that%20trades%20at%20a%20higher%20multiple.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-invest-10000-investing-tips-stock-market