0over%20time%2C%20and%20cycles%20of%20joy%20and%20pain%20are%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Faverage-stock-market-return%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eheartbeat%20of%20the%20stock%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20all%20know%20words%20ring%20hollow%20when%20you're%20out%20of%20a%20job%20and%20financial%20stability%20feels%20unattainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20remember%20how%20cyclical%20the%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20and%20your%20fortune%20%E2%80%94%20can%20be.%20AI%2C%20like%20other%20technologies%2C%20may%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20society%20rather%20than%20a%20downfall.%20Its%20cannibalization%20of%20entry-level%20jobs%20may%20be%20overstated.%20Sure%2C%20you%20could%20find%20some%20evidence%20of%20companies%20automating%20roles%2C%20but%20the%20slowdown%20in%20hiring%20looks%20to%20be%20more%20than%20in%20AI-concentrated%20fields.%20This%20looks%20more%20like%20your%20run-of-the-mill%20job%20market%20slump%2C%20something%20we've%20encountered%20plenty%20of%20times%20in%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEconomists%20are%20split%20on%20what's%20happening%20%E2%80%94%20and%20what%20comes%20next.%20Stanford%20researchers%20claim%20AI%20is%20already%20gobbling%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-broke-graduate-hiring-city-executive-warns-gen-z-revolt-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eentry-level%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20noticeable%20rate%2C%20while%20Yale%20Budget%20Lab%20analysts%20argue%20there's%20no%20evidence%20of%20this%20in%20employment%20and%20unemployment%20data.%20MIT%20researchers%20have%20found%20that%20a%20vast%20majority%20of%20AI%20implementations%20in%20businesses%20fail%20to%20generate%20profits%2C%20and%20a%20Harvard%20Business%20Review%20study%20found%20that%20AI%20output%20is%20actually%20harming%20worker%20productivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverybody%20seems%20to%20be%20grasping%20for%20narratives%2C%20which%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20natural%20human%20response%20during%20a%20time%20of%20drastic%20change.%20Add%20in%20a%20revolutionary%20technology%2C%20and%20the%20noise%20is%20deafening.%20Right%20now%20%E2%80%94%20as%20it%20was%20in%20the%20late%201990s%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20hard%20to%20put%20a%20finger%20on%20what%20forces%20will%20prevail%20over%20the%20next%20decades.%20But%20if%20AI%20proves%20to%20be%20like%20every%20other%20technological%20breakthrough%2C%20it'll%20help%20us%20become%20better%20at%20our%20jobs%20and%20lead%20to%20lower%20unemployment.%20Yes%2C%20even%20if%20it%20takes%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can't%20just%20wait%20for%20the%20economic%20tide%20to%20pick%20you%20up%2C%20though.%20If%20we%20really%20are%20coming%20under%20AI's%20technological%20grip%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20skills%20that%20humanize%20you.%20Become%20a%20commodity%20in%20an%20increasingly%20homogenous%20world.%20Focus%20on%20empathy%2C%20communication%2C%20and%20strategy%20to%20set%20yourself%20apart.%20On%20the%20financial%20side%2C%20learn%20to%20be%20an%20owner%2C%20not%20an%20employee.%20While%20you%20initially%20need%20to%20make%20money%20to%20have%20money%2C%20the%20days%20of%20climbing%20the%20corporate%20ladder%20are%20long%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20The%20average%20worker's%20paycheck%20grew%20by%205%25%20each%20year%2C%20slightly%20faster%20than%20the%204%25%20growth%20in%20prices.%20But%20if%20you%20invested%20in%20a%20hypothetical%2C%20no-fee%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20fund%2C%20you%20would've%20made%2015%25%20annual%20returns%20on%20your%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FxGlwM%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22breakout-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Split%20Bars%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FxGlwM%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%