%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20essay%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffree-solo-climber-alex-honnold-career-path-climate-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAlex%20Honnold%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20professional%20rock%20climber%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20Honnold%20Foundation.%20Honnold's%20rope-free%20ascent%20of%20the%203%2C000-foot%20rock%20wall%20El%20Capitan%20in%20Yosemite%20National%20Park%20was%20featured%20in%20the%20Oscar-winning%202018%20documentary%20%26quot%3BFree%20Solo.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHonnold%20is%20an%20executive%20producer%20and%20host%20of%20the%20podcast%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fus%2Fpodcast%2Fplanet-visionaries-season-5%2Fid1572495128%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPlanet%20Visionaries%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20spotlights%20pioneering%20conservationists%20addressing%20the%20impacts%20of%20climate%20change.%20The%20podcast%2C%20produced%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20Rolex%20Perpetual%20Planet%20Initiative%2C%20returns%20for%20its%20fifth%20season%20on%20October%2028.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHonnold%2C%2040%2C%20lives%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20two%20daughters.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a58c99aa-f13d-4b87-b897-71414b340f3e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20drop%20my%20daughter%20off%20at%20school%2C%20then%20I%20climb%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wake%20up%20and%20I%20have%20my%20green%20juice%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupplements-peter-attia-takes-longevity-anti-aging-magnesium-vitamin-d-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAthletic%20Greens%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20a%20powder%20you%20mix%20with%20water.%20I%20live%20in%20the%20desert%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20nice%20morning%20routine%20because%20you%20just%20drink%20a%20bunch%20of%20water%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20never%20been%20into%20coffee.%20I%20think%20it%20tastes%20disgusting.%20I%20try%20to%20get%20enough%20sleep.%20I%20eat%20relatively%20well.%20I%20try%20to%20exercise%20enough.%20So%20it%20all%20works%20pretty%20well%20without%20caffeine.%20I%20normally%20wake%20up%20feeling%20rested%20and%20fired%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20my%20juice%2C%20I%20eat%20some%20breakfast%2C%20which%20is%20usually%20either%20muesli%20and%20fruit%20or%20eggs%2C%20toast%2C%20and%20avocado.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20I%20go%20outside%20and%20go%20climbing.%20I%20probably%20climb%20more%20than%20most%20climbers%2C%20around%2030%20to%2040%20hours%20a%20week.%20It%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20working%20a%20full-time%20job%2C%20though%2C%20because%20it's%20so%20freaking%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20living%20at%20home%20with%20my%20family%2C%20I%20often%20take%20my%20older%20daughter%20to%20school%2C%20drop%20her%20off%2C%20and%20then%20head%20to%20a%20nearby%20cliff%2C%20where%20I%20climb%20until%20pick-up%20time.%20I%20then%20pick%20her%20up%20on%20the%20way%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20day%20is%20either%20a%20climbing%20day%20or%20a%20rest%20day%20for%20me.%20Traditionally%2C%20I%20follow%20a%20two-day-on%2C%20one-day-off%20routine.%20Rest%20days%20are%20different%20every%20day%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20mean%20bed%20rest.%20It%20just%20means%20resting%20your%20skin%20and%20physically%20resting%20your%20muscles.%20It's%20nice%20to%20do%20mentally%20engaging%20work%20on%20rest%20days%2C%20such%20as%20hosting%20podcasts%2C%20working%20with%20my%20foundation%2C%20public%20speaking%2C%20and%20all%20the%20other%20activities%20that%20accompany%20being%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftommy-caldwell-learned-trauma-surviving-kidnapping-kyrgyzstan-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprofessional%20climber%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Power%20Hours%20series%20gives%20readers%20an%20inside%20look%20at%20how%20powerful%20leaders%20in%20business%20structure%20their%20workday.%20See%20more%20stories%20from%20the%20series%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpower-hours-day-in-the-life-successful-business-leaders-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20reach%20out%20to%20editor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Flauryn-haas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELauryn%20Haas%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20share%20your%20daily%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fbc79051-b992-414a-8083-81c116c0bcdb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20routine%20always%20changes%2C%20but%20I%20have%20one%20non-negotiable%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20of%20being%20a%20professional%20climber%20is%20that%20you're%20sponsored%20because%20you're%20good%20at%20the%20sport%2C%20but%20then%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20you're%20getting%20paid%20to%20show%20up%20at%20events%20and%20do%20public%20appearances%2C%20so%20I%20travel%20all%20the%20time%20for%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alex%20Honnold%20and%20a%20partner%20hiking%20through%20a%20red%20canyon.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68fc0103c007ca8c2737a189%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlex%20Honnold%2C%20right%2C%20approaching%20a%20climb%20in%20Red%20Rock%20Canyon%20National%20Conservation%20Area%20near%20Las%20Vegas.%3Cp%3EBrian%20van%20der%20Brug%2FLos%20Angeles%20Times%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20ways%2C%20I'm%20very%20routine%2C%20as%20I%20eat%20and%20drink%20the%20same%20things%20all%20the%20time.%20But%20in%20the%20bigger%20picture%2C%20I%20travel%20so%20much%20that%20sometimes%20I%2