20Dubai.%20At%20SuperReturn%20Middle%20East%20%E2%80%94%20a%20private%20capital%20conference%20in%20the%20UAE's%20largest%20city%20%E2%80%94%20he%20noted%20that%20local%20references%20and%20long-term%20relationships%20matter%20more%20than%20flashy%20PowerPoint%20presentations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETransactions%20and%20fundraising%20are%20relationship-driven%2C%20according%20to%20both%20fund%20allocators%20and%20investing%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20many%20GPs%20fly%20in%20for%20a%20day%20and%20expect%20a%20check%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Awaiz%20Patni%2C%20chief%20financial%20officer%20of%20a%20Saudi%20Arabia-based%20family%20office%2C%20at%20the%20SuperReturn%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoney%20will%20only%20come%20if%20you%20build%20a%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f9931cd-1e47-41e5-ae21-ca1e3de4991e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOffices%20aren't%20necessary%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20visit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMillennium%2C%20Brevan%20Howard%2C%20Schonfeld%2C%20and%20ExodusPoint%20are%20just%20a%20few%20of%20the%20hedge%20funds%20that%20have%20opened%20offices%20in%20either%20Abu%20Dhabi%20or%20Dubai.%20Many%20funds%20have%20also%20been%20driven%20to%20open%20offices%20in%20the%20region%20because%20their%20employees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-funds-talent-middle-east-capital-dubai-abu-dhabi-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewant%20to%20live%20there%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20tax-free%20status%20and%20warm%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20local%20fundraiser%20for%20emerging%20hedge%20funds%20in%20Dubai%2C%20who%20spoke%20anonymously%20because%20his%20firm%20does%20not%20allow%20them%20to%20speak%20publicly%2C%20said%20the%20notion%20that%20the%20region's%20sovereign%20wealth%20funds%20require%20a%20physical%20office%20to%20get%20capital%20is%20misguided.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20Mark%20Oshida%2C%20the%20regional%20head%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20Africa%20for%20the%20consulting%20firm%20Cambridge%20Associates%2C%20said%20his%20firm%20has%20counted%20many%20of%20the%20large%20sovereigns%20as%20clients%20for%20years%2C%20but%20they%20never%20pushed%20the%20organization%20to%20hang%20a%20shingle%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOshida%2C%20who%20moved%20to%20Dubai%20in%20April%2C%20said%20the%20organization%20decided%20to%20have%20a%20physical%20presence%20once%20it%20started%20working%20with%20more%20local%20family%20offices%2C%20including%20many%20run%20by%20Europeans%20or%20Asians%20who%20relocated%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20tax%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20an%20actual%20office%20isn't%20required%2C%20fundraisers%20and%20investors%20in%20the%20region%20both%20say%20that%20to%20get%20money%20and%20do%20deals%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20you%20need%20more%20than%20a%20Zoom%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222366%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Arabic%20coffee%20cart%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68fe773ac007ca8c2737a60b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221774%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20cart%20of%20Arabic%20coffee%20at%20the%20SuperReturn%20Middle%20East%20event.%3Cp%3EBradley%20Saacks%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20be%20present%2C%20physically%20present%2C%26quot%3B%20Sawhney%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharles%20Myers%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20research%20firm%20Signum%20Global%20Advisors%2C%20who%20splits%20his%20time%20between%20New%20York%20and%20London%2C%20began%20his%20Wednesday%20talk%20at%20the%20AIM%20Summit%20in%20Dubai%20by%20noting%20that%20it%20was%20his%20fifth%20visit%20to%20the%20Gulf%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20would%20prefer%20to%20just%20move%20to%20the%20region%20instead%20of%20constantly%20taking%20flights%20from%20Europe%2C%20Asia%2C%20or%20the%20US%2C%20especially%20if%20it's%20a%20focus%20for%20their%20firms%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20transactions%20here%20do%20take%20longer%20than%20other%20places%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Taimoor%20Labib%2C%20founding%20partner%20and%20head%20of%20MENA%20for%20private%20equity%20manager%20Affirma%20Capital%2C%20at%20SuperReturn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMax%20Burke%2C%20a%20director%20at%20Actis%20who%20moved%20to%20Dubai%20from%20London%2C%20is%20a%20private-equity%20investor%20focused%20on%20infrastructure%20projects%20like%20data%20centers.%20He%20believes%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20opportunities%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20but%20warned%20at%20the%20SuperReturn%20conference%20that%20dealmakers%20should%20be%20prepared%20for%20many%20breakfasts%2C%20lunches%2C%20coffees%2C%20and%20dinners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226caf679e-8e10-4c7b-885f-6ccdc02a3d58%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearn%20the%20culture%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELearn%20to%20love%20the%20coffee%20%E2%80%94%20which%2C%20if%20it's%20traditional%2C%20is%20served%20unfiltered%20from%20a%20dallah%20pot%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20come%20to%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20alcohol%20is%20now%20legal%20and%20sold%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20region%2C%20such%20as%20Dubai%20and%20the%20Qatari%20capital%20Doha%2C%20business%20has%20been%20done%20over%20coffee%20for%20centuries%2C%20several%20locals%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20study%20the%20region%20from%20a%20cultural%20perspective%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Khalil%20Chami%2C%20CFO%20of%20Ali%20%26amp%3B%20Sons%2C%20a%20Dubai-based%20conglomerate%20that%20also%20invests%20through%20international%20asset%20managers%2C%20at%20SuperReturn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20just%20here%20for%20a%20transaction%2C%20we%20can%20tell%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20a%20Westernized%20city%20like%20Dubai%2C%20traditions%20matter.%20SuperReturn%20rolled%20out%20an%20Arabic%20coffee%20cart%20for%20attendees.%20One%20fundraiser%20for%20an%20international%20firm%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20London%20and%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous%2C%20said%20they%20also%20make%20a%20point%20of%20telling%20any%20Middle%20Easterners%20they%20meet%20with%20that%20they%20buy%20coffee%20from%20the%20region%20to%20bring%20home%20to%20their%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20long%20timelines%20to%20make%20decisions%20are%20not%20just%20because%20they%20want%20to%20frustrate%20visitors%2C%20several%20locals%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20see%20if%20your%20values%20align%20with%20ours%2C%26quot%3B%20family%20office%20executive%20Patni%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20region%20has%20the%20wealth%20the%20Middle%20East%20does%2C%20it%20brings%20a%20certain%20class%20of%20conmen%20and%20get-rich-quick%20dreamers.%20Spotting%20scammers%20is%20just%20as%20important%20as%20finding%20a%20good%20opportunity%2C%20Chami%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWarburg's%20Sawhney%20said%20the%20three%20values%20people%20looking%20to%20do%20deals%20in%20the%20region%20should%20keep%20in%20mind%20are%20patience%2C%20flexibility%2C%20and%20humility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20see%20all%20three%20present%20all%20the%20time%20in%20the%20West%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20of%20course%2C%20%26quot%3Bget%20used%20to%20Arabic%20coffee%2C%26quot%3B%20Chami%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fasset-managers-middle-east-relationships-fundraising-coffee-trust-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1761552901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68fbe3dd0be9845f2dc51656%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fasset-managers-middle-east-relationships-fundraising-coffee-trust-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Global%20asset%20managers%20are%20racing%20to%20tap%20the%20Middle%20East's%20trillions%20in%20wealth.%20Locals%20share%20what%20will%2