ding%20decisions%20or%20executive%20overreach%2C%20but%20it's%20unlikely%20that%20they%20would%20see%20an%20outcome%20any%20time%20soon%20because%20of%20how%20long%20the%20legal%20process%20takes.%20And%20Congress%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20move%20forward%20until%20it%20decides%20on%20a%20temporary%20budget%20to%20reopen%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20is%20that%20the%20courts%20are%20not%20particularly%20set%20up%20to%20prevent%20illegality%20here%2C%20they're%20set%20up%20to%20declare%20reality%20happened%20after%20the%20fact%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Connor%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20have%20funding%20decisions%2C%20getting%20a%20decision%20two%20years%20after%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20should%20have%20spent%20funds%20in%20some%20way%20is%20not%20particularly%20helpful.%20Because%20the%20damage%20has%20been%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-has-been-making-major-funding-decisions-without-congress-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1761552541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68fb86020be9845f2dc50841%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-has-been-making-major-funding-decisions-without-congress-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20has%20control%20of%20federal%20spending.%20During%20the%20government%20shutdown%2C%20Trump%20is%20changing%20that.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22allisonkelly%40businessinsider.com%20(Allie%20Kelly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A48%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-has-been-making-major-funding-decisions-without-congress-2025-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98emotional%20infidelity%E2%80%99%20remark%20resurfaces%3B%20netizens%20react%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A176155235200