20success%20is%20whether%20it%20actually%20serves%20users%20and%20solves%20a%20problem%20for%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20focus%20on%20what%20we're%20trying%20to%20build%20and%20whom%20we're%20trying%20to%20build%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAll%20this%20code%20can%20be%20thrown%20away%20tomorrow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrasanna%20also%20said%20that%20it's%20not%20important%20to%20be%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20every%20technological%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTechnology%20is%20here%20to%20serve%20us%2C%20and%20if%20we%20have%20an%20important%20reason%20for%20being%20and%20an%20important%20purpose%2C%20then%20we%20can%20make%20it%20that%20technology%20serve%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrasanna%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2273685e8c-6240-403d-854b-7995f05b96f5%5C%22%3ECoding%20apocalypse%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPrasanna's%20comments%20come%20as%20tech%20leaders%20continue%20to%20emphasize%20the%20importance%20of%20coding%20in%20the%20AI%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-research-head-career-advice-learn-to-code-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20head%20of%20research%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Yossi%20Matias%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20last%20year%20that%20%26quot%3Beverybody%20should%20learn%20how%20to%20code%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20basics%20may%20be%20more%20critical%20than%20ever%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbluesky-ceo-ai-dont-outsource-thinking-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBluesky%20CEO%20Jay%20Graber%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20July%20that%20people%20need%20to%20know%20how%20to%20code%20well.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20know%20what%20good%20code%20looks%20like%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20actually%20build%20a%20system%2C