-traces-uss-nimitz-sailor-says-worse-problem-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUSS%20Nimitz%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20went%20down%2030%20minutes%20apart%20from%20each%20other%20during%20routine%20operations%2C%20the%20Navy%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20personnel%20involved%20are%20safe%20and%20in%20stable%20condition.%20The%20cause%20of%20both%20incidents%20is%20currently%20under%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20statement%2C%20the%20Sea%20Hawk%20was%20the%20first%20to%20go%20down%20at%20about%202.45%20p.m.%20local%20time.%20It%20was%20assigned%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BBattle%20Cats%26quot%3B%20of%20Helicopter%20Maritime%20Strike%20Squadron%2073.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20crew%20members%20on%20board%20were%20later%20rescued%2C%20the%20Navy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Super%20Hornet%2C%20from%20the%20%26quot%3BFighting%20Redcocks%26quot%3B%20of%20Strike%20Fighter%20Squadron%2022%2C%20crashed%20at%203%3A15%20p.m.%2C%20per%20the%20Navy.%20The%20statement%20added%20that%20both%20crew%20members%20had%20ejected%20just%20before%20the%20fighter%20jet%20went%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20separate%20incidents%20come%20as%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20engages%20in%20a%20diplomatic%20tour%20in%20Asia%20this%20week%2C%20which%20he%20kick-started%20with%20a%20meeting%20in%20Malaysia%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tour%20is%20expected%20to%20include%20a%20leg%20in%20China%2C%20where%20Trump%20is%20scheduled%20to%20meet%20China's%20leader%2C%20Xi%20Jinping.%20Trade%20is%20high%20on%20the%20agenda%20as%20the%20Trump%20administration%20threatens%20severe%20tariffs%20on%20China%20and%20tensions%20between%20Washington%20and%20Beijing%20continue%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETreasury%20Secretary%20Scott%20Bessent%20suggested%20on%20Sunday%20that%20the%20US%20may%20hold%20back%20on%20plans%20to%20impose%20100%25%20tariffs%20on%20China%20after%20Trump's%20preliminary%20talks%20with%20Beijing