try%20as%20a%20technology%20analyst%20for%20Gavekal%20Dragonomics%2C%20a%20financial%20services%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20now%20a%20research%20fellow%20at%20Stanford%20University's%20Hoover%20Institution.%20Wang%20published%20his%20first%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BBreakneck%3A%20China's%20Quest%20to%20Engineer%20the%20Future%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20said%20the%20EV%20price%20war%20in%20the%20country%20won't%20stop%20anytime%20soon%2C%20and%20that's%20by%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20too%20many%20entrepreneurs%2C%20too%20many%20engineers%2C%20and%20too%20much%20desire%20for%20local%20governments%20to%20support%20local%20champions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBrutal%20competition%20has%20produced%20many%20of%20China's%20successes%2C%20for%20example%2C%20in%20solar%20and%20electric%20vehicles.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20reason%20for%20many%20of%20these%20industries%20to%20have%20low%20profits%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20wrote%20in%20%26quot%3BBreakneck%26quot%3B%20that%20government%20support%20was%20a%20key%20reason%20Chinese%20tech%20giants%20like%20Huawei%20and%20Xiaomi%20ventured%20into%20the%20automotive%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20sort%20of%20expansion%20is%20driven%20both%20by%20the%20fiercely%20competitive%20market%20environments%20and%20by%20government%20subsidies%20that%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20companies%20to%20try%20their%20hand%20at%20making%20new%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20allow%20companies%20to%20unleash%20a%20flood%20of%20undifferentiated%20products%2C%20ruthlessly%20underbid%20each%20other%2C%20and%20pray%20their%20competitors%20run%20out%20of%20money%20before%20they%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20race%20to%20the%20bottom%20is%20starting%20to%20show%20up%20in%20EV%20companies'%20bottom%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20BYD%20said%20its%20net%20profit%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20fell%20by%2030%25%20from%20a%20year%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBYD%20said%20in%20its%20earnings%20report%20that%20%26quot%3Bshort-term%20profitability%26quot%3B%20had%20been%20pulled%20down%20by%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbyd-share-price-slumps-analysts-gravy-train-slowing-chinese-ev-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexcessive%20marketing%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20discounting.%20In%20May%2C%20BYD%20said%20it%20was%20slashing%20prices%20on%2022%20electric%20and%20hybrid%20models%20until%20the%20end%20of%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompetition%20in%20China%20is%20cutthroat%2C%20and%20it's%20hard%20for%20that%20situation%20to%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20partly%20a%20function%20of%20the%20giant%20scale%20of%20China's%20market%2C%20in%20which%20entrepreneurs%20are%20always%20daring%20to%20pursue%20opportunities%2C%20which%20is%20a%20feature%20of%20China's%20highly%20dynamic%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b375e34c-42fe-40e5-b47d-911b5b6c7b0f%5C%22%3EHundreds%20of%20billions%20in%20subsidies%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20US's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECenter%20for%20Strategic%20%26amp%3B%20International%20Studies%20said%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-electric-vehicles-government-subsidies-win-ev-race-byd-tesla-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20China's%20government%20had%20spent%20at%20least%20%24230%20billion%20since%202009%20supporting%20local%20EV%20champions%20such%20as%20BYD.%20The%20think%20tank%20said%20the%20figure%20was%20probably%20an%20underestimate%2C%20since%20it%20did%20not%20include%20incentives%20and%20subsidies%20from%20regional%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERivian%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frivian-ceo-china-evs-low-cost-competition-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERJ%20Scaringe%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20the%20%26quot%3BEverything%20Electric%26quot%3B%20podcast%20in%20an%20episode%20that%20aired%20in%20September%20that%20China's%20EVs%20are%20cheaper%20because%20of%20the%20country's%20generous%20subsidies%20and%20lower%20labor%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20not%20something%20magical%20when%20you%20take%20it%20apart%20that's%20allowing%20these%20really%20impressive%20cost%20structures%2C%26quot%3B%20Scaringe%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20secret%20magic%20thing%20that%20you're%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20aha%2C%20they%20did%20this.'%20But%20rather%20it's%20the%20compounding%20benefits%20of%20a%20lower%20cost%20of%20capital.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20everybody%20has%20said%20that%20China's%20EV%20market%20will%20remain%20as%20hotly%20contested%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20Xpeng%20CEO%20He%20Xiaopeng%20told%20his%20staff%20that%20the%20auto%20industry%20would%20experience%20an%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxpeng-ceo-2025-2027-kick-off-ev-industry-elimination-round-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eelimination%20round%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20from%202025%20to%202027%2C%20per%20an%20internal%20letter%20obtained%20by%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Xpeng%20founder%20said%20in%20a%20November%20interview%20with%20Singaporean%20newspaper%20The%20Straits%20Times%20that%20most%20Chinese%20automakers%20won't%20survive%20past%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20personally%20think%20that%20there%20will%20only%20be%20seven%20major%20car%20companies%20that%20will%20exist%20in%20the%20coming%2010%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20without%20naming%20specific%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-china-watcher-ev-market-too-many-entrepreneurs-engineers-2025-9%5C%2