Cp%3EFor%20more%20than%2018%20years%2C%20Wei%20Khjan%20Chan%20has%20worked%20as%20an%20accountant%2C%20a%20profession%20often%20flagged%20as%20being%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpwc-ai-training-changing-the-job-accountants-jenn-kosar-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erisk%20of%20automation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Each%20time%20he%20saw%20headlines%20warning%20that%20AI%20could%20replace%20jobs%20like%20his%2C%20he%20said%20he%20felt%20the%20pressure%20mounting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt'll%20be%20great%20if%20I%20get%20to%20know%20AI%20earlier.%20At%20least%20I%20replace%20myself%20rather%20than%20let%20other%20people%20replace%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2039-year-old%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20stay%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve%2C%20Chan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-limits-use-cases-software-companies-airtable-redis-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epicked%20up%20vibe%20coding%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20using%20AI%20tools%20to%20write%20code%20and%20build%20apps.%20The%20audit%20partner%20at%20an%20accounting%20and%20advisory%20firm%20in%20Malaysia%20said%20he%20stumbled%20on%20vibe%20coding%20in%20June%20after%20attending%20weekend%20coding%20workshops%20in%20Singapore%20and%20Malaysia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20having%20no%20technical%20background%2C%20Chan%20built%20a%20web%20app%20to%20solve%20a%20pain%20point%20in%20his%20professional%20life%3A%20filing%20expense%20claims%20after%20business%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20uses%20AI-powered%20optical%20character%20recognition%20to%20scan%20and%20process%20receipts%2C%20automatically%20exporting%20them%20into%20files%20for%20his%20company's%20finance%20teams.%20He's%20also%20using%20AI%20to%20automate%20his%20workflow%2C%20such%20as%20generating%20invoices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20code%20is%20a%20bunch%20of%20JavaScript%2C%20which%20obviously%20I%20don't%20understand%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20showing%20Business%20Insider%20his%20web%20app.%20%26quot%3BWithout%20the%20vibe%20coding%20tools%20and%20the%20skill%20set%2C%20an%20accountant%20is%20unable%20to%20do%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217df3185-ff09-4683-a18d-f297018c757e%5C%22%3EAI%20isn't%20a%20ticket%20out%20of%20accounting%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20how%20to%20save%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20accountant%20said%20he%20didn't%20learn%20vibe%20coding%20to%20make%20a%20career%20switch.%20Instead%2C%20he%20sees%20%26quot%3BAI%20know-how%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20fundamental%20skill%20for%20any%20office%20profession%2C%20like%20Excel.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20his%20own%20apps%20showed%20him%20just%20how%20powerful%20the%20tools%20can%20be%3A%20what%20once%20required%20weeks%20and%20an%20entire%20team%20to%20build%20as%20a%20proof%20of%20concept%20can%20now%20be%20prototyped%20in%20a%20single%20weekend%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChan%20also%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he's%20advocating%20for%20broader%20adoption.%20As%20a%20committee%20member%20in%20his%20local%20accounting%20institute%20in%20Malaysia%2C%20he's%20lobbying%20for%20more%20AI%20training%20at%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faccountant-shortage-sexy-taxes-business-school-pwc-kpmg-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFewer%20people%20are%20pursuing%20accountancy%20%3C%2Fa%3Eeven%20as%20demand%20for%20accounting%20services%20rises.%20With%20manpower%20falling%20short%2C%20AI%20could%20help%20fill%20the%20gap%2C%20Chan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22309000b0-b024-4c68-870d-c0931e931899%5C%22%3ELessons%20learned%20from%20vibe%20coding%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChan%20said%20that%20when%20he%20first%20started%20experimenting%20with%20AI%2C%20he%20was%20advised%20to%20write%20long%2C%20detailed%20prompts%20with%20%26quot%3Bfull%20context%20length.%26quot%3B%20But%20experience%20taught%20him%20that%20smaller%2C%20iterative%20steps%20work%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3